      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s looking\u2014and driving\u2014like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I can't wait for you to get behind the wheel and see for yourself!",
