    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the legendary S54B32 straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and optimized by a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures precise torque vectoring. The chassis remains structurally flawless\u2014subframe reinforcement is documented\u2014and the suspension geometry is strictly OEM. Finished in pristine Laguna Seca Blue over Nappa leather, this is a turnkey collector piece for the discerning purist.",
