      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that remains in breathtaking, showroom condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring the exterior paint retains a deep, glass-like luster completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. The body panels are laser-straight with perfect gaps throughout. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership; the premium upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that fresh, signature interior scent. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, operates with factory precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service record performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. It comes complete with the original window sticker, all sets of keys, and factory manuals. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key example that looks and performs exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
